#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_iro_management
msgid ""
"Disclosure requirements in ESRS covered by the undertaking's\n"
"                        sustainability statement (IRO-2)"
msgstr ""
"ຂໍ້ກຳນົດການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນໃນ ESRS ທີ່ກວມເອົາໂດຍຖະແຫຼງການຄວາມຍືນຍົງ\n"
"                        ຂອງອົງກອນ (IRO-2)"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_basic_for_prepation
msgid "Disclosures in relation to specific circumstances [BP-2]"
msgstr "ການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບສະຖານະການສະເພາະ [BP-2]"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_iro_management
msgid "Disclosures on the materiality assessment process"
msgstr "ການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນກ່ຽວກັບຂະບວນການປະເມີນຄວາມສຳຄັນ"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_vsm_c6
