msgid ""
"Effluent quality is tracked through laboratory testing and local water\n"
"                authority reports. Marine-related data (e.g., discharge, waste into marine areas)\n"
"                are monitored in line with national regulations and international frameworks (e.g.,\n"
"                EU Water Framework Directive, Marine Strategy Framework Directive)."
msgstr ""
"ຄຸນນະພາບຂອງນ້ຳເສຍແມ່ນໄດ້ຖືກຕິດຕາມຜ່ານການທົດສອບໃນຫ້ອງທົດລອງ ແລະ ລາຍງານຈາກ\n"
