#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_vsm_c3
msgid ""
"Highlight targeted outcomes for each action (e.g., reduction in tCO₂eq, "
"efficiency improvements, renewable energy adoption)."
