#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_vsm_b3
msgid ""
"Scope 3 categories such as employee commuting are estimated using employee-reported home-to-work distances, commuting modes, vehicle characteristics where applicable,\n"
"                        and the organisation's homeworking policy to account only for days worked on site. Additional indirect emissions not directly linked to accounting daa,\n"
"                        such as refrigerant gases, employee meals, or waste management, may be manually added using documented activity data and standard emission factors.\n"
"                        When only estimates or partial information are available, the company applies reasonable assumptions consistent with VSME guidance."
msgstr ""
"ໝວດໝູ່ຂອບເຂດທີ 3 ເຊັ່ນ: ການເດີນທາງຂອງພະນັກງານ ແມ່ນໄດ້ຮັບການຄາດຄະເນໂດຍນຳໃຊ້ໄລຍະທາງຈາກເຮືອນ"
"ຫາບ່ອນເຮັດວຽກທີ່ພະນັກງານແຈ້ງ, \n"
"                        ຮູບແບບການເດີນທາງ, ລັກສະນະຂອງພາຫະນະ (ຖ້າມີ), ແລະ ນະໂຍບາຍການ"
"ເຮັດວຽກຢູ່ເຮືອນຂອງອົງກອນ ເພື່ອນັບສະເພາະມື້ທີ່ເຮັດວຽກຢູ່ສະຖານທີ່. \n"
"                        ການປ່ອຍອາຍພິດທາງອ້ອມເພີ່ມເຕີມທີ່ບໍ່ໄດ້ເຊື່ອມໂຍງໂດຍກົງກັບຂໍ້ມູນການບັນຊີ ເຊັ່"
"ນ: ກ໊າຊທຳຄວາມເຢັນ, ອາຫານຂອງພະນັກງານ, \n"
