"The requirements of this section should be read in conjunction with the\n"
"                            disclosures required by ESRS 2:"
msgstr ""
"ຂໍ້ກຳນົດຂອງພາກນີ້ຄວນອ່ານຄຽງຄູ່ກັບ\n"
"                            ການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ກຳນົດໂດຍ ESRS 2:"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_e1
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_e2
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_e3
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_e4
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_s1
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_s2
msgid ""
"The requirements of this section should be read in conjunction with the\n"
"                        disclosures\n"
"                        required by ESRS 2:"
msgstr ""
"ຂໍ້ກຳນົດຂອງພາກນີ້ຄວນອ່ານຄຽງຄູ່ກັບ\n"
"                        ການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນ\n"
"                        ທີ່ກຳນົດໂດຍ ESRS 2:"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_e5
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_g1
msgid ""
"The requirements of this section should be read in conjunction with the\n"
"                        disclosures required by ESRS 2:"
msgstr ""
"ຂໍ້ກຳນົດຂອງພາກນີ້ຄວນອ່ານຄຽງຄູ່ກັບ\n"
"                        ການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ກຳນົດໂດຍ ESRS 2:"

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_governance
msgid ""
"The responsibilities of the governance bodies include validation of\n"
"                        sustainability\n"
"                        targets, long-term roadmaps, short-term action plans, and key performance\n"
"                        indicators\n"
"                        across all material ESG topics. Oversight is exercised through designated\n"
"                        committees, reporting lines, and internal controls integrated with broader\n"
"                        management and risk functions."
msgstr ""
"ຄວາມຮັບຜິດຊອບຂອງຄະນະກຳມະການຄຸ້ມຄອງ ລວມມີການກວດສອບຢັ້ງຢືນ\n"
"                        ເປົ້າໝາຍຄວາມຍືນຍົງ,\n"
"                        ແຜນວາດໄລຍະຍາວ, ແຜນດຳເນີນງານໄລຍະສັ້ນ, ແລະ ຕົວຊີ້ວັດຜົນການດຳເນີນ"
"ງານ\n"
"                        ຫຼັກ\n"
"                        ໃນທຸກຫົວຂໍ້ ESG ທີ່ສຳຄັນ. ການກວດກາແມ່ນດຳເນີນຜ່ານຄະນະກຳມະການ\n"
"                        ທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບມອບໝາຍ, ສາຍການລາຍງານ, ແລະ ການຄວບຄຸມພາຍໃນ ທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງ"
"ເຂົ້າກັບ\n"
"                        ໜ່ວຍງານຄຸ້ມຄອງ ແລະ ຄວາມສ່ຽງໃນວົງກວ້າງ."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_s4
msgid ""
"The resulting disclosures shall be presented alongside those required by\n"
"                            ESRS 2, except for <strong>ESRS 2 SBM-3 - Material impacts, risks and\n"
"                            opportunities and\n"
"                                their interaction with strategy and business model(s)</strong>, for\n"
"                            which the undertaking may present the disclosures\n"
"                                alongside the topical disclosure."
msgstr ""
"ການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບຈະຖືກນຳສະເໜີຄຽງຄູ່ກັບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ກຳນົດໂດຍ\n"
"                            ESRS 2, ຍົກເວັ້ນ <strong>ESRS 2 SBM-3 - ຜົນກະທົບ, ຄວາມ"
"ສ່ຽງ, ແລະ\n"
"                            ໂອກາດທີ່ສຳຄັນ ແລະ\n"
"                                ການພົວພັນກັບຍຸດທະສາດ ແລະ ຮູບແບບທຸລະກິດ</strong>, ເຊິ່"
"ງ\n"
"                            ອົງກອນອາດຈະນຳສະເໜີການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນນັ້ນ\n"
"                                ຄຽງຄູ່ກັບການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນຕາມຫົວຂໍ້."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_s3
msgid ""
"The resulting disclosures shall be presented alongside those required by\n"
"                            ESRS 2, except for <strong>ESRS 2 SBM-3 - Material impacts, risks and\n"
"                            opportunities and\n"
"                                their interaction with strategy and business model(s)</strong>, for\n"
"                            which the undertaking may present the disclosures alongside the topical disclosure."
msgstr ""
"ການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ໄດ້ຮັບຈະຖືກນຳສະເໜີຄຽງຄູ່ກັບຂໍ້ມູນທີ່ກຳນົດໂດຍ\n"
"                            ESRS 2, ຍົກເວັ້ນ <strong>ESRS 2 SBM-3 - ຜົນກະທົບ, ຄວາມ"
"ສ່ຽງ, ແລະ\n"
"                            ໂອກາດທີ່ສຳຄັນ ແລະ\n"
"                                ການພົວພັນກັບຍຸດທະສາດ ແລະ ຮູບແບບທຸລະກິດ</strong>, ເຊິ່ງ"
"ອົງກອນອາດຈະນຳສະເໜີການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນນັ້ນຄຽງຄູ່ກັບການເປີດເຜີຍຂໍ້ມູນຕາມຫົວຂໍ້."

#. module: esg_csrd
#: model_terms:knowledge.article,template_body:esg_csrd.esg_csrd_knowledge_article_template_csrd_esrs_e5
msgid ""
"The resulting disclosures shall be presented alongside those required by\n"
"                        ESRS 2, except for <strong>ESRS 2 SBM-3 - Material impacts, risks and\n"
"                        opportunities and\n"
"                            their interaction with strategy and business model(s)</strong>, for\n"
"                        which the undertaking may present the disclosures\n"
"                            alongside the topical disclosure."
